quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,Enywe Abandu banje muli murie ebalanganga khubuhonia nanyu munaanganga okhutsia mumulilo
  40,42,"Munaanganga mbu ekhaye Nyasaye mana emutsokasie khukengorerwe , nasi emulanganga khu owa Amaani Owobulesheli muno"
  40,43,"Toto\towamunanjilanga okhumulaama shakhoyesheele okhukholelwa omulango khushialo khuno nohomba mwikulu tawe, ne efwe fwesi khulikalusibwa ewa Nyasaye , ne toto balia babura eshichelo nibo Abandu bomumulilo"
  40,44,"Ne mulitsulila kebaboolelanga kano ne endeshela likhuwa lianje Nyasaye, toto Nyasaye alolanga muno Abasumba bebe"
  40,45,"Mana Nyasaye nabaliinda khubusuku bwabakhola, mana eshinyasio eshibii shilibotokhana Abandu ba Firaun"
  40,46,"Balinjila mumulilo itsuli nende ingoloobe ne olwa indukho iliula baliboolelwa mbu: “injisie Abandu ba Firauni mushinyasio eshilulu”"
  40,47,"Olwa balireebana mumulilo, Abateshele balireeba Abafuru mbu: “ toto efwe khwabaloondangakhwo mana munyala okhukhututuyiliakhwo omulilo kuno.”"
  40,48,"Abafuru baliboola mbu: “ toto efwe fwesi khulimwo , toto Nyasaye amalile okhubusia khubandu bebe”"
  40,49,"Balia bali mumulilo baliboolela abalindi bomulilo mbu: “ mukhusabilekhwo Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi , akhututuyiliekhwo eshinyasio kata inyanga ndala.”"
  40,50,"Baliboola mbu: “Abarumwa shibabeetselanga nende ebifune biahabulafu? Baliboola mbu: “kali kario” mana baliboolelwa mbu: “ musabe Nyasaye wenyu, ne amalaamo kabakhayi ni amakhaya imbeli wa Nyasaye"
  40,51,"Toto efwe khulihabina Abarumwa befu nende balia basuubila khushialo, nende inyanga yabaloli balieema"
  40,52,"Inyanga yebichila biabakhayi shibiliwulilwa tawe, ne balinyoola eshitsubo, ne balinyoola eshimenyo eshibi muno"
  40,53,Netoto khwahelesia Musa obulunjifu ne nikhuhelesia Abana ba Israil eshitabu
  40,54,Shilimwo obulunjifu nende emetsulisio khu bandu bamachesi
  40,55,"Kho wisumilisie toto aka Nyasaye yalaka kalirulila, ne saba eshileshelo khumabii ko, ne witsomie Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ingoloobe nende itsuli"
  40,56,"Toto balia bayingananga khubimanyisio bia Nyasaye nibabula amatililo , ebilifu biabu nebikhaya halali benyanga obukhongo ne shibanyala okhubuulila tawe, kho wilinde khu Nyasaye , toto ye ni Omuwulili Omuloli muno"
  40,57,"Toto okhulongwa khwelikulu nende eshialo nokhukhongo okhushila okhulongwa khwa Abandu, halali Abandu abanji shibamanyile tawe"
  40,58,"Ne shibahelaana omuwofu nende owulolanga tawe, nohomba balia abasuubila nibakhola amalayi bakhayelana nende abetsimbi? Muparanga hatiti muno"
  40,59,"Toto indukho iliula ibula obukanakani tawe, halali Abandu abanji shibasuubilanga tawe"
  40,60,"Ne Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi yaboola mbu: “musabee ndalabahelesia, toto balia belolanga okhulaama esie balinjila mumulilo nibatutuye.”"
  40,61,"Nyasaye niye wabakholela eshilo muhulushilemwo, ne eshitere mulolele, toto Nyasaye niwetsimbabaasi khubandu halali Abandu abanji shibakhupanga orio tawe"
  40,62,"Oyo niye Nyasaye wenyu omulesi owaloonga buli eshindu , abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali ye tawe, kho ni hena amuhenjibungwa"
  40,63,Ne endio nilwa baliinjibwa balia abakhayanga ebimanyisio biefu
  40,64,"Nyasaye niye wabakholela eshialo okhuba eshimenyo , ne likulu okhuba eshiumbashe , mana nabahelesia ifwani indayi muno, ne nabahelesia emikabo emilayi muno , oyo niye Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu , ne niwoluyali Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje biosi"
  40,65,"Naye Nomulamu abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali Ye , khomumulaame mubutwenufu, oluyali nilwa Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi"